These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
City: berlin, nizza, hannover, colone
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is between Beverage:cola and City:nizza##2
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of City:berlin##3
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is somewhere between Beverage:tea and Beverage:cola##7
4. City:nizza is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:tea is on the right of City:hannover##1
6. City:nizza is somewhere to the left of City:berlin##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| City      | hannover  | nizza | colone        | berlin |

