.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
Birthday: july, december, march, february
Sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. Sport:volleyball is somewhere between Sport:skateboarding and Birthday:march##7
2. Birthday:february is somewhere to the left of Birthday:july##5
3. Birthday:february is somewhere to the right of Sport:volleyball##5
4. Birthday:december is on the left of Birthday:february##1
5. Sport:volleyball is between Sport:skateboarding and Sport:rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Birthday     | march | december       | february         | july     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

