2. Hobby:collecting is somewhere between Flower:iris and Hobby:writing##7
3. Hobby:woodworking == Flower:orchid##1
4. Flower:daisy is on the left of Flower:orchid##1
5. Hobby:traveling is on the left of Flower:azalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
